---
title: Sesame Chicken Noodles with green beans and chilli pepper
description: The toasted sesame seeds are an amazing complement to the sesame oil-based teriyaki sauce in this recipe. Perfectly cooked green beans add a slightly crunchy texture to this Asian-inspired noodle dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230131_R12_W12_IE_IEXQC0088-2_Main_high-8ee605cf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/sesame-chicken-noodles-63b4064b749d7fa20bf999f9-5fe34235.pdf
